{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hey, is Regina here!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I sure am. But Boss, shouldn't you knock first?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "The last time you barged in here, I was fresh out of the shower and still naked."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fc,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, sorry. I'm just not good at doing fancy things, like knocking on doors."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I don't think knocking is all that fancy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Well, don't worry, your naked body was as noticeable as a pebble on the ground to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "That still kinda hurts..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It's not like you to get hurt from that. If you really didn't like that, try yelling \"kyaaah\" or something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hmm? Oh, I didn't know you had a guest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I'm Ayesha. Regina's been looking after me for a while now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "How polite of you. I'm Glide, the boss of this prospecting site."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, what a pretty missy. Hey, Regina..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I'll knock before coming in from now on..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Please make sure you do. It would've been even worse if Ayesha was in the shower."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "By the way, why did you come here today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I almost forgot. We're gonna have a party soon, so get ready."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x125,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Again? We just had one not that long ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Huh? A party? Soon...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "The nuisances in the ruin are increasing again, so we've decided to go thin them out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Thinning out the slags...<CR>No matter how many times we do it,<CR>there's no end to them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "We've dug pretty deep, so we might've hit a nest of slags somewhere..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fa,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "So that's about it.<CR>Come out to the plaza later on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Sorry, Ayesha.<CR>I guess I have plans now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "So the party is about exterminating slags? Seems like quite a bother..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Well, it's part of my job. If their numbers increase, they'll just get in our way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Basically, once a month, all the prospectors get together and do a big sweep."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "So, it's kinda like a party for us prospectors."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "But party makes it sound like it's gonna be fun."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, they like to fool around.<CR>A whole bunch of stupid guys like<CR>to do this kind of work, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "If you're interested, why don't you come out to the plaza?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Well, I guess I should be going then!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "(Exterminating slags... I wonder how it's done. I...might be interested...)"
        }
    ]
}